    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into the underwater world of Sonar Scout, where you navigate a lonely submarine tasked with exploring the depths to activate lost beacons in order to restore connection to a forgotten civilization.  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179560/extras/c34026a44ff1c26db93b3df417441a42.poster.avif?t=1728922051\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179560/extras/c34026a44ff1c26db93b3df417441a42.webm?t=1728922051\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179560/extras/c34026a44ff1c26db93b3df417441a42.mp4?t=1728922051\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your keen sense of navigation and ability to memorize the landscape will be vital to survival. Beware, you aren't alone  and quick reflexes might save you from the hazards down below.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179560/extras/647f8d5432161c1f6cb523b5d36d259e.poster.avif?t=1728922051\" width=600 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179560/extras/647f8d5432161c1f6cb523b5d36d259e.webm?t=1728922051\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179560/extras/647f8d5432161c1f6cb523b5d36d259e.mp4?t=1728922051\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you explore new environments you’ll unlock new submarines with unique abilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179560/extras/13eeaee5e9412b3e3b86e326d623334a.poster.avif?t=1728922051\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179560/extras/13eeaee5e9412b3e3b86e326d623334a.webm?t=1728922051\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179560/extras/13eeaee5e9412b3e3b86e326d623334a.mp4?t=1728922051\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Think you can master the depths faster than your friends? Display it proudly on the leaderboards and challenge them to prove you wrong!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179560/extras/f02345333a681606799033c4cc1cfa34.poster.avif?t=1728922051\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179560/extras/f02345333a681606799033c4cc1cfa34.webm?t=1728922051\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179560/extras/f02345333a681606799033c4cc1cfa34.mp4?t=1728922051\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sonar Scout was made by a team of 6 developers from 5 different countries who all met at Spelkollektivet, a co-living space for game developers located in Sweden. We'd love for you to join us on Discord where you can offer feedback and compete in challenge runs with the community for a chance to win a copy of the game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179560/extras/e7b9284488413d634c87b41e80ac854a.avif?t=1728922051\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179560/extras_big/e7b9284488413d634c87b41e80ac854a.avif?t=1728922051 width=800 height=618 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
